<!doctype html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Cetak BAST - <%= distribution.asset_code %></title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif, sans-serif;
      color: #000;
      line-height: 1.35;
      margin: 15px 30px;
      background-color: #fff;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    .no-print-bar {
      background-color: #f3f4f6;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .btn {
      padding: 6px 12px;
      font-family: sans-serif;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 500;
      border-radius: 6px;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      border: none;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      background-color: #1e3a8a;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover {
      background-color: #1d4ed8;
    }
    .btn-outline {
      background-color: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
      color: #374151;
    }
    .btn-outline:hover {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
    }
    .letterhead {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      border-bottom: 2px double #000;
      padding-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .letterhead h1 {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin: 0 0 2px 0;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .letterhead p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #374151;
    }
    .title-doc {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .title-doc h2 {
      font-size: 14px;
      margin: 0 0 2px 0;
      text-decoration: underline;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .title-doc p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .content-section {
      font-size: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      text-align: justify;
    }
    .identity-table {
      width: 100%;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .identity-table td {
      padding: 2px 0;
      vertical-align: top;
    }
    .identity-table td.label-col {
      width: 180px;
    }
    .identity-table td.separator-col {
      width: 15px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .asset-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin-top: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .asset-table th, .asset-table td {
      border: 1px solid #000;
      padding: 6px;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .asset-table th {
      background-color: #f2f2f2;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .signature-container {
      margin-top: 25px;
      width: 100%;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .signature-box {
      width: 40%;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .signature-space {
      height: 50px;
    }
    .signature-box p {
      margin: 3px 0;
    }
    @page {
      size: auto;
      margin: 0mm;
    }
    @media print {
      .no-print {
        display: none !important;
      }
      body {
        margin: 1.6cm 2cm;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Floating Navigation / Print Action (Hidden on Print) -->
  <div class="no-print-bar no-print">
    <div style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563;">
      Format BAST - Siap Cetak
    </div>
    <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px;">
      <button onclick="window.history.back()" class="btn-outline">
        ← Kembali
      </button>
      <button onclick="window.print()" class="btn btn-primary">
        🖨️ Cetak ke PDF / Kertas
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Kop Surat Resmi (Letterhead) -->
  <div class="letterhead-container" style="display: flex; align-items: center; border-bottom: 3px double #000; padding-bottom: 8px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <div style="flex-shrink: 0; margin-right: 15px;">
      <img src="/assets/images/logo_unand.png" alt="Logo Unand" style="width: 80px; height: 80px; object-fit: contain;" />
    </div>
    <div style="flex-grow: 1; text-align: center;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 12px; font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; font-weight: bold; margin: 0; text-transform: uppercase; color: #000; line-height: 1.2;">KEMENTERIAN PENDIDIKAN TINGGI, SAINS DAN TEKNOLOGI</h2>
      <h1 style="font-size: 15px; font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; font-weight: bold; margin: 2px 0 0 0; text-transform: uppercase; color: #000; line-height: 1.2;">UNIVERSITAS ANDALAS</h1>
      <h1 style="font-size: 15px; font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; font-weight: bold; margin: 2px 0 0 0; text-transform: uppercase; color: #000; line-height: 1.2;">FAKULTAS TEKNOLOGI INFORMASI</h1>
      <p style="font-size: 10px; margin: 4px 0 0 0; line-height: 1.3; color: #000; font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;">
        Kampus Universitas Andalas, Limau Manis, Padang - 25163<br />
        website: <span style="text-decoration: underline;">http://fti.unand.ac.id</span> email: sekretariat@it.unand.ac.id
      </p>
    </div>
    <!-- Empty block to balance the logo flex centering -->
    <div style="width: 80px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-left: 15px;" class="no-print-placeholder"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Judul Dokumen BAST -->
  <div class="title-doc">
    <h2>BERITA ACARA SERAH TERIMA ASET</h2>
    <p>Nomor: BAST/<%= new Date(distribution.distribution_date).getFullYear() %>/00<%= distribution.id %></p>
  </div>

  <div class="content-section">
    Pada hari ini, tanggal <%= new Date(distribution.distribution_date).toLocaleDateString('id-ID', { day: '2-digit', month: 'long', year: 'numeric' }) %>, bertempat di Universitas Andalas, kami yang bertanda tangan di bawah ini:
  </div>

  <!-- Pihak Pertama (Pemberi) -->
  <table class="identity-table">
    <tr>
      <td class="label-col"><strong>I. Nama</strong></td>
      <td class="separator-col">:</td>
      <td><%= distribution.allocator_name %></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td class="label-col">Jabatan</td>
      <td class="separator-col">:</td>
      <td>Pengelola Aset (Pihak Pertama)</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td class="label-col">Email</td>
      <td class="separator-col">:</td>
      <td><%= distribution.allocator_email || '-' %></td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <!-- Pihak Kedua (Penerima) -->
  <table class="identity-table">
    <tr>
      <td class="label-col"><strong>II. Nama</strong></td>
      <td class="separator-col">:</td>
      <td><%= distribution.recipient_name %></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td class="label-col">Jabatan</td>
      <td class="separator-col">:</td>
      <td>Penerima Aset (Pihak Kedua)</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td class="label-col">Email</td>
      <td class="separator-col">:</td>
      <td><%= distribution.recipient_email || '-' %></td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <div class="content-section">
    Pihak Pertama menyerahkan kepada Pihak Kedua, dan Pihak Kedua menyatakan telah menerima aset dalam kondisi baik/sesuai keterangan di bawah ini untuk digunakan guna kepentingan operasional institusi:
  </div>

  <!-- Rincian Aset -->
  <table class="asset-table">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th style="width: 250px;">Nama Aset</th>
        <th>Rincian Spesifikasi / Serial Number</th>
        <th>Kondisi</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>
          <strong><%= distribution.asset_name %></strong><br />
          <span style="font-size: 12px; color: #444;">Kode: <%= distribution.asset_code %></span>
        </td>
        <td>
          <strong>Brand:</strong> <%= distribution.brand || '-' %><br />
          <strong>Model:</strong> <%= distribution.model || '-' %><br />
          <strong>Serial Number:</strong> <%= distribution.serial_number || '-' %><br />
          <strong>Spesifikasi:</strong> <%= distribution.specification || '-' %>
        </td>
        <td>
          <% if (distribution.asset_condition === 'good') { %>
            Baik
          <% } else if (distribution.asset_condition === 'minor_damage') { %>
            Rusak Ringan
          <% } else if (distribution.asset_condition === 'major_damage') { %>
            Rusak Berat
          <% } else { %>
            <%= distribution.asset_condition || '-' %>
          <% } %>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <div class="content-section">
    <strong>Catatan Penyerahan:</strong><br />
    <%= distribution.notes || 'Tidak ada catatan khusus.' %>
  </div>

  <div class="content-section" style="margin-top: 20px;">
    Demikian Berita Acara Serah Terima Aset ini dibuat dengan sebenar-benarnya untuk digunakan sebagaimana mestinya. Pihak Kedua berkewajiban merawat, menjaga, dan mengembalikan aset tersebut apabila sudah tidak digunakan lagi atau masa tugas telah berakhir.
  </div>

  <!-- Tanda Tangan -->
  <div class="signature-container">
    <div class="signature-box">
      <p>Yang Menerima,</p>
      <p><strong>Pihak Kedua</strong></p>
      <div class="signature-space"></div>
      <p><strong><u><%= distribution.recipient_name %></u></strong></p>
      <p>NIP/NIDN. ..................................</p>
    </div>
    <div class="signature-box">
      <p>Yang Menyerahkan,</p>
      <p><strong>Pihak Pertama</strong></p>
      <div class="signature-space"></div>
      <p><strong><u><%= distribution.allocator_name %></u></strong></p>
      <p>NIP. ..................................</p>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
